info.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued October 19 at 9:57AM PDT until October 19 at 12:00PM PDT by NWS Oxnard
info.description: ...DENSE FOG ADVISORY NOW IN EFFECT UNTIL NOON PDT TODAY... * WHAT...Visibility one quarter mile or less in dense fog. * WHERE...San Luis Obispo County Beaches, San Luis Obispo County Inland Central Coast, Santa Barbara County Central Coast Beaches and Santa Barbara County Inland Central Coast. * WHEN...Until noon PDT today. * IMPACTS...Very low visibility will create dangerous driving conditions, especially Highway 1.
info.instruction: If driving, slow down, use your headlights, and leave plenty of distance ahead of you.
